        h2 Event Media Distribution
        .feature  Share your media with newsrooms around the world instantly. Maximize exposure for your event.
      #details.col-md-4.animated.fadeIn
        h2 Asset Management
        .feature  Archive media into one, easy-to-access platform. Manage and sort large amounts of content into multiple galleries and folders.
      #details.col-md-4.animated.fadeIn
        h2 Business Solutions
        .feature  Distribute training videos and documents. Keep track of who is viewing what or even granting access to certain employees.

section.home-features
