    #missioncontrol.row.featureRow.wow.animated.fadeInLeft
      .col-md-6
        h2 Mission Control for your videos
        .feature Create a themeable content portal with as many galleries you need. Share videos outside of your gallery by using embed codes to post your video on webistes and social media. 
      .col-md-6
        .feature
          img.img-responsive src="http://placehold.it/565x320" alt="Mission Control for Videos"
    #security.row.featureRow.wow.animated.fadeInRight
      .col-md-6
        .feature
          img.img-responsive src="http://placehold.it/565x320" alt="Security Features"
      .col-md-6
        h2 Security
        .feature Keep your videos both secure and private with our security and privacy settings. Password protect media, hide folders from the public and allow exclusive access.
    #analytics.row.featureRow.wow.animated.fadeInLeft
      .col-md-6
        h2 Analytics
        .feature Keep track of how, where and when your videos are being viewed. Yeah science!
      .col-md-6
        .feature
